<h2 id="add-a-site-selector-module-to-a-page" sourcefile="articles/commerce/site-selector.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">Add a site selector module to a page</h2>
<p sourcefile="articles/commerce/site-selector.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">The site selector module can be added to the <a href="author-header-module.html" sourcefile="articles/commerce/site-selector.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">Header module</a> under the site selector slot. After it's added, you can define the module heading and site options.</p>
